|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|- style=\"border-top:2px solid #aaaaaa\"\n!rowspan=2| \n|rowspan=2 align=left| {{flagicon|FRA}} CIP Green Power\n| 40\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;\"| Ret\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n!rowspan=2| 0\n|-\n| 73\n|style=\"background:#cfcfff;\"| 27\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|- style=\"border-top:2px solid #aaaaaa\"\n! Pos\n! Team\n! Bike<br>No.\n! [[2020 Qatar motorcycle Grand Prix|QAT]]<br>{{flagicon|QTR}}\n! [[2020 French motorcycle Grand Prix|FRA]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}}\n! [[2020 Italian motorcycle Grand Prix|ITA]]<br>{{flagicon|ITA}}\n! [[2020 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|CAT]]<br>{{flagicon|CAT}}\n! [[2020 German motorcycle Grand Prix|GER]]<br>{{flagicon|DEU}}\n! [[2020 Dutch TT|NED]]<br>{{flagicon|NLD}}\n! [[2020 Finnish motorcycle Grand Prix|FIN]]<br>{{flagicon|FIN}}\n! [[2020 Czech Republic motorcycle Grand Prix|CZE]]<br>{{flagicon|CZE}}\n! [[2020 Austrian motorcycle Grand Prix|AUT]]<br>{{flagicon|AUT}}\n! [[2020 British motorcycle Grand Prix|GBR]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}}\n! [[2020 San Marino and Rimini's Coast motorcycle Grand Prix|RSM]]<br>{{flagicon|SMR}}\n! [[2020 Aragon motorcycle Grand Prix|ARA]]<br>{{flagicon|Aragon}}\n! [[2020 Thailand motorcycle Grand Prix|THA]]<br>{{flagicon|THA}}\n! [[2020 Japanese motorcycle Grand Prix|JPN]]<br>{{flagicon|JPN}}\n! [[2020 Australian motorcycle Grand Prix|AUS]]<br>{{flagicon|AUS}}\n! [[2020 Malaysian motorcycle Grand Prix|MAL]]<br>{{flagicon|MYS}}\n! [[2020 Motorcycle Grand Prix of the Americas|AME]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}}\n! [[2020 Argentine motorcycle Grand Prix|ARG]]<br>{{flagicon|ARG}}\n! [[2020 Valencian Community motorcycle Grand Prix|VAL]]<br>{{flagicon|Valencia}}\n! [[2020 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|ESP]]<br>{{flagicon|ESP}}\n! Pts\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Grand Prix motorcycle racing}}\n{{World championships in 2020}}\n\n[[Category:2020 in Grand Prix motorcycle racing|Moto3]]\n[[Category:Grand Prix motorcycle racing 